overview: In this DVD magazine, entitled "Hello! Project Desktop Competition 2021", two people picked up from a total of 26 people from ANGERME, Juice=Juice, and Tsubaki Factory will play one-on-one seriously! ?? The commentary will be delivered by Joujou Gundan! Disc 1 (105mins), Disc 2 (92mins).
title: Hello! Project DVD Magazine Vol.68
